; Regression test for GitHub issue #1029
; A transaction using lot price annotation {price} must still balance
; in the base commodity. Ledger was incorrectly accepting imbalanced
; transactions because it treated "Avios {1.00 bmi}" and "Avios" as
; two separate currencies and auto-assigned a conversion.

2014-01-25 * Received bmi points from MBNA credit card
    Assets:bmi                           2500.00 bmi
    Income:Rewards

2014-02-27 * Received Avios from Diamond Club on BAEC account
    Assets:ba                             2500 Avios @@ 2500.00 bmi
    Assets:bmi                          -2500.00 bmi

2014-03-29 * Received Avios from BA credit card
    Assets:ba                              200 Avios
    Income:Rewards

2014-05-08 * Spend Avios
    Expenses:Flights                      3000 Avios
    Assets:ba                           -2500 Avios {1.00 bmi} [2014/02/27]
    Assets:ba                             -200 Avios

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 22:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 19-22:
> 2014-05-08 * Spend Avios
>     Expenses:Flights                      3000 Avios
>     Assets:ba                           -2500 Avios {1.00 bmi} [2014/02/27]
>     Assets:ba                             -200 Avios
Unbalanced remainder is:
          2800 Avios
-2500 Avios {1.00 bmi} [2014/02/27]
